  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Management of Synthetic Disease-modifying Antirheumatic Drug (DMARD) at the Onset of Adverse Events, Intolerance or Lack of Efficacy in Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA)</brief_title>
  <acronym>SAR-FAME</acronym>
  <official_title>A Retrospective, Multicentre Observational Study to Assess the Management of Synthetic Disease-modifying Antirheumatic Drug (DMARD) at the Onset of Adverse Events, Intolerance or Lack of Efficacy in Real Life in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
