  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find patterns in the use of non-biological DMARDs as the
      initial treatment of RA and how adverse events (AEs), intolerance or lack of efficacy may
      impact therapeutic decisions in real life in the Spanish Andalusian region.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
