    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients of both sexes ≥ 18 years.

          -  Patients diagnosed with RA (according to the American College of Rheumatology (ACR)
             2010 criteria) between January 2008 and December 2012 and who have initiated treatment
             with at least one synthetic DMARD during that period.

          -  Patients who have given written informed consent for their data to be collected and
             reviewed.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who are already participating in a clinical trial/s at the moment of
             participation in this study.

          -  Patients with whom it is suspected there will be insufficient information to complete
             the study objectives.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
